"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/631204","Department for International Development","false","2016-11-15","<p>In 2014-15, the top 10 recipients of the Departments contractual funds were:</p><p>Crown Agents, PWC, Adam Smith International, Mott MacDonald, DAI Europe, Palladium, Voluntary Services Overseas, Oxford Policy Management, Coffey International and Population Services International.</p>","Penrith and The Border","Rory Stewart",,"2016-11-15T15:28:31.743Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/631204/answer","Biography information for Rory Stewart","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/631204/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/631204/answer",,,,,"20","International Development","International Development","2016-11-07","Department for International Development: Procurement","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Development, which organisations were the top 10 recipients of her Department's contractual funds in 2014-15.","false","Biography information for Stephen Twigg","Liverpool, West Derby","Stephen Twigg","52073"
